
describe-user-profiles
**********************


DESCRIPTION
===========

Describe specified users.


SYNOPSIS
========

   aws opsworks describe-user-profiles
     --iam-user-arns <value>


REQUIRED PARAMETERS
===================

"--iam-user-arns"  (list of string)
   An array of IAM user ARNs that identify the users to be described.

   *Parameter Syntax*

      ["string", ...]


OPTIONAL PARAMETERS
===================

None
